- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture): The paper proposes a new design for a memory cell, which falls under the scope of hardware architecture. 
- cs.EM (Electromagnetism): The paper discusses the use of resistive networks in the proposed memory cell, which falls under the scope of electromagnetism.
